        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Tissue from a living forest troll has been integrated through this hide armor. This armor has two organic receptacles on its back that can each hold a single elixir of life. One elixir takes 3 Interact actions to install. For the armor to function properly, each elixir must be the same level.",
